org.kite.annotations

Annotation Type AsyncMethod


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface AsyncMethod
    Methods marked with this annotation, will be called asynchronously, if Provided.async() instance has AsyncType.METHODS or AsyncType.ALL type.
    See Also:
    Provided, AsyncResult

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      int value
      Code of the given async method.

    • Element Detail

      • value

        public abstract int value
        Code of the given async method. Must be unique inside declaring interface. AsyncResult callback methods will be called by this code.
        Default:
        0
